snippet.textDisplay: A very, very long time ago, there was an incident during a live performance where Heechul's voice cracked (stuff happens). After that he was severely criticized. The criticism was so bad, he stepped back from singing, which is unfortunate because we now see what we've been deprived of a very good singer for many years. Unfortunately, his old injury is what now holds him back from performing with SuJu since he feels bad that he might be holding back their performances which involves rigorous dance routines. At least he can still perform ballads with the members and other artists. His solo song Old Movie is pretty good too.

The criticism was so bad, he stepped back from singing, which is unfortunate because we now see what we've been deprived of a very good singer for many years. Unfortunately, his old injury is what now holds him back from performing with SuJu since he feels bad that he might be holding back their performances which involves rigorous dance routines. At least he can still perform ballads with the members and other artists. His solo song Old Movie is pretty good too.
